# SavnithFreedom
## Newly Remastered!

### SavnithFreedomMod
SavnithFreedomMod was founded by Savnith (AlphaGaming). It was created to the ease of movement of TotalFreedomMod as it uses tfm and fop it's going to be on its own mod! Developed by Savnith, as it the mod is as important as the server. SavnithFreedom was made on the date November 12, 2015 and it was a beta server on Fadehost after the month of November we have lost payments to Fadehost so the server has been inactive with the mod unfinished! We are in desperate need of Admins and developers!
